.Dt SYSCON 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm syscon
.Nd SYSCON reset and power off
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "syscon* at fdt?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides for system reset and power off functionality through
a generic system configuration (SYSCON) interface.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr intro 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 6.1 .
